title: Nellie Women's Co-ord Set
description:

title: Oversized Estelle Summer Co-ord Set
description:
Product Description Manufacture, Care and Fit The Nobero monotone co-ord set is a stylish and
comfortable clothing ensemble designed specifically for women. It features a cropped top and
elasticated shorts, offering both comfort and a sleek appearance. The set is characterized by its
monotone color scheme, adding a touch of elegance and versatility to the overall look. Whether
you're lounging at home, running errands, or traveling, this co-ord set provides a fashionable and
relaxed outfit option. Fit Type: Relaxed Fit Fabric: 60% Cotton, 40% Polyester Care Instructions:
Machine Wash, Wash Dark Colours Together

title: Monotone Comfort Co-ord
description:
Product Description Manufacture, Care and Fit A chic monochrome ensemble, perfect for the
fashionable woman. The crop top boasts a sophisticated crew neckline and full sleeves, with an
elasticated waistband and cuff for a flattering fit. The high-rise joggers feature a regular fit,
adjustable waist, and drawcord detailing, with a crisp cuffed hem and two practical side pockets.
Both functional and stylish, this co-ord set is a must-have for the modern woman seeking effortless
elegance.Fabric : Soft, Stretchy Baby Fleece. 100% rich, breathable cotton | 240 GSM. Care : Machine
wash according to instructions on care label.

Product Description Manufacture, Care and Fit The Nobero monotone co-ord set is a stylish and
comfortable clothing ensemble designed specifically for women. It features a sleeveless t-shirt and
elasticated shorts, offering both comfort and a sleek appearance. The set is characterised by its
monotone colour scheme, adding a touch of elegance and versatility to the overall look. Whether
you're lounging at home, running errands, or travelling, this co-ord set provides a fashionable and
relaxed outfit option. Fit Type: Regular Fit Fabric: 60% Cotton, 40% Polyester Care Instructions:
Machine Wash, Wash Dark Colours Together

title: Oversized Sloane Summer Set
description:
Product Description Manufacture, Care and Fit Introducing our luxurious Cosy Loungewear Collection
- the ultimate loungewear for summer. Made from a unique blend of viscose, polyester, and elastane,
this collection boasts a buttery-soft, ultra-comfortable knitted jersey fabric that feels as amazing
as it looks.Experience the epitome of comfort and style with our easy-breezy silhouettes and wide
range of colors, perfect for lounging around the house or running errands in style. The attention to
detail is reflected in every piece, from the delicate stitching to the luxurious texture of the
fabric.Whether you're curling up with a good book or entertaining guests, our Cosy Loungewear
Collection is sure to impress. Relax in style and stay cool and comfortable during hot summer days
with this premium collection. Elevate your loungewear game and shop our collection today. Product
Detail : Sloane consists of a set of boxy-fit top & regular-fit shorts with an elasticated
waistband. The top features a crew neck while the bottoms are equipped with two deep side
pockets.Fabric : Knitted jersey in an unique blend of viscose polyester & elastane | 190 GSM.Care :
Machine wash according to instructions on care label.
